bes the LP as an embodiment of “renewal and growth, mirroring her evolving artistry and the album&#39;s thematic voyage through life&#39;s intricate phases.”</p><p> In other plans for 2025, the Mercury Prize and <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">BRIT</a> award-winning rapper will <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-confirmed-to-curate-meltdown-2025-at-londons-southbank-3837337">be curating a boundary-breaking line-up for this year&#39;s edition of the 11-day London festival</a> , Meltdown. As well as organising performances across the weekends, Simz is <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-to-play-one-off-orchestral-show-at-londons-meltdown-2025-as-first-line-up-announced-3848673">set to play a one-off orchestral show</a> at the event.</p><p> Alongside live performances, it will also include two weekends of free participatory programming featuring grassroots collectives and local organisations. <a href="https://www.southbankcentre.co.uk/events/meltdown/?gad_source=1&amp;gbraid=0AAAAAq2-4xpBer1a3AAhaQtvRe3g0Nk8U&amp;gclid=CjwKCAjw47i_BhBTEiwAaJfPpukvnRumQz4hT5YyM477Z4zN59l76QGGME-_ELwB13fGW_SYab_-YRoCcK8QAvD_BwE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit here</a> for tickets.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-announces-biggest-uk-live-shows-london-manchester-arena-gigs-buy-tickets-3851521">Little Simz announces biggest UK live shows to date with London and Manchester arena gigs</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
